title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report. 
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report.
2. Navigate to the table containing highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data.
OB: When attempting to export data from the table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown during the process. The exception occurs in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' function.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should be successful without any exceptions. The data should be exported.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table containing highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data.
